{"tid":2123814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟據報將限制向香港出口可用於鎮壓及監視的技術","createTime":"2020-07-25T03:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T07:28:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f65d2e0a04f0b29816ecb03860dc72b5a0d5cf3f","tid":2123814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539765-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539765-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=2bb2ef71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539765-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7e7336ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539765-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟27國對北京在香港實施「港區國安法」表示「嚴重關切」，同意採取一系列制裁措施，包括貿易限制和檢討簽證協議。路透社引述歐盟一份文件草稿稱，歐盟將限制向香港出口可用於鎮壓或監視的設備和技術。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟重申支持香港自治及其公民，並承諾進一步與香港的民間社會接觸。<br />\n<br />\n獲歐盟各國大使支持的文件提到，歐盟將進一步審視，以及限制向香港出口特定敏感設備和技術，特別是有理由懷疑相關設備和技術可用於內部鎮壓，截取通訊或網絡監視。<br />\n<br />\n文件可望於下周二生效。<br />\n<br />\n文件說，歐盟還致力考慮「港區國安法」對庇護、移民、簽證和居留政策的影響。歐盟暫時不會與香港展開新的磋商，並將檢視「港區國安法」對歐盟與香港現有協議的影響。"},{"pid":"7b0d9000a7b0a28500d6d64b3e87c07ebef90449","tid":2123814,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"用國貨囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167d352ba4c8717773632c9be3d7a7a2c8078535","tid":2123814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0d9000a7b0a28500d6d64b3e87c07ebef90449","tid":2123814,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"用國貨囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"中國國貨的技術 (晶片) 都係來自西方"},{"pid":"8dd112d705bac53b72ba9c650c020347f17d5996","tid":2123814,"uid":103981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"舊年都係玩下外交照會<br />\n今次直接制裁<br />\n林太真係底氣十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc8853ba9702018c0918b5df5325b982268f01c","tid":2123814,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dd112d705bac53b72ba9c650c020347f17d5996","tid":2123814,"uid":103981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"舊年都係玩下外交照會<br />\n今次直接制裁<br />\n林太真係底氣十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:24:35.000Z","msg":"佢棋子黎啫。你估佢有實權咩"},{"pid":"cf82157fd5181f995dfe1b07991a5bbe72984ddc","tid":2123814,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"據報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超過一年啦，仲諗"},{"pid":"4f86dd93eb63fdfaa41611f2e1e54ca884dfad9b","tid":2123814,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"太遲了<br />\n不過都算做左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec74c6c13f63c910d6683d187db93653490d3b7b","tid":2123814,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"香港冇左逃犯互引，冇左特別關稅，又冇得入口先進科技<br />\n但多左國家安全，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}